      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HELLO PECK (1) made a big impression on debut when was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a 1.75 lengths second (22.47) over 388m at this track. Looks promising and rates on top here on debut effort. HIGH DEGREES (4) made an eye-catching debut when showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 5 lengths over 388m this track in 22.56. Can only be improved and looks a key chance if runs up to debut effort. PRINCESS ENERGY (8) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and is long overdue for a win, having placed 13 of 23 career runs. In the money at the last three runs. Bold showing expected. SHAMEFUL (2) returns after a break and looks a top-three hope.",
